title: Good Omens REACTION Series PREMIERE: In the Beginning
author: JK Reacts
comment: I LOVE your Eddie Izzard shirt! 😍

Oh I wish I saw y'all's reactions to The marvelous Miss Maizel so few people have reacted to it.
If y'all are okay with shows that have smaller viewing numbers like under a thousand for say 3 months or so then Frankie and Grace or Grace and Frankie.
It's about two women who are elderly and their husbands are work partners and end up coming out as gay together and the two women have extremely different personalities.
Never wanted to be that guy, but Good Omens isn't in Discworld. But it's also a collab with Terry Pratchett & Neil Gaiman. Have Fun, I loved the series.
